attributes.description:
The DShield Honeypot is a low interaction honeypot that allows the Internet Storm Center to collect data for research purposes. The honeypot by default runs the following clients: 

- Collecting SSH and Telnet usernames and passwords via Cowrie
 - An HTTP honeypot collecting full http requests
 - We also collect firewall logs from the honeypot
